SUMMARY:Gentle Yoga (Guild Room)
DESCRIPTION:Come build community through 45 minutes of chair yoga. Seated in a chair\, we will move gently\, mindfully\, stretching\, and finding our alignment both internally and externally. Breath is emphasized as is a smile. Modifications are always provided\, and we move at a pace that is appropriate for all levels and all ages. \nZOOM
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/gentle-yoga-guild-room-3-5/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:Guild Room
CATEGORIES:All Church Events,All Events,Featured Events,Small Groups
