SUMMARY:Pilgrimage to Delaney Hall (Offsite)
DESCRIPTION:Journey With Us On A Good Friday Pilgrimage To Delaney Hall On Friday\, April 3\, from 8am-3pm\, or join us along the way! \nJoin us on an ecumenical Good Friday journey from Montclair to Delaney Hall\, the ICE detention center in Newark. Together\, we will pray with our feet\, show solidarity with our immigrant neighbors\, and bear witness to the cruelty towards and crucifixion of immigrants today. Join us for the first section\, the last section\, or the culminating prayer service at Delaney Hall\, 451 Doremus Avenue\, Newark. View full details (including the sections you can participate in) at bit.ly/DelaneyHallPilgrimage or scan QR code below. \n 
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/pilgrimage-to-delaney-hall-offsite/
LOCATION:Off Site
CATEGORIES:All Church Events,All Events,Featured Events,Justice & Community Engagement
ORGANIZER;CN="Union Congregational Event":MAILTO:contact@unioncong.org
END:VEVENT
